1.8
log
@Untangle abstract sleep modes from ACPI sleep states. This paves the way
for further work in the area.

idea and ok deraadt
ok mlarkin
@
text
@/* $OpenBSD: acpitoshiba.c,v 1.7 2017/02/25 20:09:20 jcs Exp $ */
/*-
